==English==
===Noun===
'''bundle'''
#A [[group]] of objects held [[together]] by [[wrapping]] or [[tying]]
#A [[package]] [[wrap]]ped or [[tied]] up for [[carry]]ing
#(''biology'') A [[cluster]] of closely [[bound]] [[muscle]] or [[nerve]] [[fibre]]s
#(''informal'') A large [[amount]], especially of [[money]]

