===Verb===
'''to bundle''' [[transitive]]
#To tie or wrap together
#To [[hustle]]; to [[dispatch]] something or someone [[quickly]]
#To [[dress]] someone [[warmly]]
#(''computing'') To [[sell]] [[hardware]] and [[software]] as a single [[product]]
'''to bundle''' [[intransitive]]
#To [[hurry]]
#To dress warmly

